queries.sql: SELECT "tb_prov"."kode_prov" as "kodeprov", "tb_prov"."nama_prov", COUNT(DISTINCT tb_khg.id) as total_khg, COUNT(DISTINCT tb_sub_khg.id) as total_sub_khg, COUNT(DISTINCT tb_hru.id) as total_hru FROM "tb_prov" LEFT JOIN "tb_khg" ON "tb_khg"."kode_prov" = "tb_prov"."kode_prov" LEFT JOIN "tb_sub_khg" ON "tb_sub_khg"."kode_khg" = "tb_khg"."kode_khg" LEFT JOIN "tb_hru" ON "tb_hru"."kode_sub_khg" = "tb_sub_khg"."kode_sub_khg" GROUP BY "tb_prov"."kode_prov", "tb_prov"."nama_prov"
